    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Used for prospecting and testing of deposits of heavy minerals. The Professional Gold Pan features riffled traps to catch your gold as the lighter material flows out of the pan, a wide textured bottom for efficient separation of your remaining black sands and deep black color to highlight even fine gold in the bottom of your pan. This light weight but super tough pan is a top-quality gold getter and will hold up to years of prospecting.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor 4 Pack 14&quot; Inch Riffled Black Gold Panning Pan Mining Sluice Tool</h2>\n  <p>Used for prospecting and testing of deposits of heavy minerals.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>Riffled Traps to Collect Minerals</li>\n    <li><strong>Material:</strong> High Impact Flexible Plastic</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Black</li>\n    <li><strong>Diameter:</strong> 14&quot;</li>\n    <li><strong>Depth:</strong> 2&quot;</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/sports_outdoors/gold_panning/pans/GP1002B_gldpan_Main.jpg\" alt=\"Used for prospecting and testing of deposits of heavy minerals\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> BB07</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 725818532955</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Black</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> 4 Pack</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>The Professional Gold Pan features riffled traps to catch your gold as the lighter material flows out of the pan, a wide textured bottom for efficient separation of your remaining black sands and deep black color to highlight even fine gold in the bottom of your pan.</p>\n  <p>This light weight but super tough pan is a top-quality gold getter and will hold up to years of prospecting.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
